  <brief_title>An Observational Study of Xeloda (Capecitabine) in Patients With Metastatic Colorectal Cancer (AXIOM)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluation of Safety and Efficacy of Xeloda in Metastatic Colorectal Carcinoma</official_title>
  <sponsors>
