  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This prospective observational study will evaluate the safety and efficacy of Xeloda
      (capecitabine) administered in monotherapy in patients with metastatic colorectal cancer.
      Patients will be followed until disease progression or unacceptable toxicity occurs.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
